{"tid":1376481,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"每日一文宣真係好L有用！","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:47:52.000Z","uid":266048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"436fa62d7a5f043ad594b0ad624bcad68dbb1374","tid":1376481,"uid":266048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"話說我母親係個師奶仔唔識亦唔太理政治<br />\n仲聽人講後生搞事信埋一份<br />\n我由13歲開始關注香港發生咩事<br />\n呢輪日日文宣我母親佢都有聽<br />\n有同佢講我訓唔到睇新聞睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事源我後父係澳門人好L紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭上台嗰日佢仲好高興添！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日到我母親文宣後父<br />\n因為佢老公靜係盲愛國<br />\n冇住過大陸<br />\n<br />\n我媽開始同佢講大饑荒同批鬥<br />\n仲有六四<br />\n母親：請問你當時身在何方?<br />\n我親身經歷過慘過，<br />\n以前我唔知覺得係啲人搞亂社會<br />\n而家我知道咩事唔係班後生你食左屎好耐喇！<br />\n愛國就應該返大陸愛！<br />\n大陸家陣有啲咩維碼微信支付你識咩?<br />\n大陸人都嫌棄你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最衰都係林鄭個婆娘搞風搞雨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢老公：⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n老母我愛你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請大家海量汪涵"},{"pid":"3a89c5af2f9e4716ab1e232503e4135db8ed3150","tid":1376481,"uid":265976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我都係咁\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"94cb84fd3c638d20331c75cac5551c395d283df0","tid":1376481,"uid":265976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9704bf47d1d4101f5c604d2d52d994cc9b78118c","tid":1376481,"uid":265976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20